displayed_text: Patient: Um hum. Doctor: I’ll tell him about you though. Patient: Okay. Doctor: But he’s coming May ninth. Patient: Alright. Don’t you leave me yet man. (Laughs) Doctor: I hope so too. He’s the man right? Patient: Yeah, yeah you’re the man but you have more grey. <____> refer me to you. Doctor: I hope that when I see you next time I will be able to give you news that yes he’s coming. Patient: Yeah, yeah. Doctor: Okay. Patient: And so, so we do this blood test all the way up until September. Doctor: Oh we’re still gonna do the blood test. I still get blood tests.
